paragraphs.title: Restaurants - Inspections by BORO
paragraphs.text:
SELECT BORO, COUNT(*) c
FROM elastic.restaurants.inspections
GROUP BY BORO
ORDER BY c DESC

paragraphs.title: Restaurants - Violation_desc contains mice or vermin
paragraphs.text:
SELECT CUISINE_DESCRIPTION, COUNT(*) c
FROM elastic.restaurants.inspections
WHERE contains(VIOLATION_DESCRIPTION:(mice OR vermin))
GROUP BY CUISINE_DESCRIPTION
ORDER BY c DESC
